author: gkossakowski
msg: COCOON-2122: Added support for calls of methods inside pipelineComponent scope (previously, each call created new scope and it led to NPEs)
COCOON-2124: Changed scope of Object Model to pipelineComponent.

* ObjectModel configuration in cocoon-expression-language-impl is just a template. Actual definition of ObjectModel bean is in cocoon-pipeline-impl because Object Model is bound to pipelineComponent scope, now.
* Redefinied ObjectModel in tests using newly introduced bean configuration template.
* Introduced PipelinecomponentScopeHolder interface, this allows me to remove dependency on cglib.
